<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>FRESH LINER | Aroma style.</title>
  <meta name="description" content="FRESH LINER - Aromatizadores con estilo. Fragancias para auto, hogar y espacios comerciales. Diseño moderno, catálogo destacado y contacto directo." />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#111111" />

  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#f7f6f2;
      --surface:#ffffff;
      --surface-2:#f0eee8;
      --text:#171717;
      --muted:#666666;
      --line:rgba(0,0,0,.10);
      --gold:#b08d2a;
      --gold-dark:#8b6b16;
      --shadow:0 14px 34px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      --radius:20px;
      --radius-sm:14px;
      --max:1220px;
    }

    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
    body{
      margin:0;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#faf9f6 0%, #f5f3ed 100%);
      color:var(--text);
      font-family:Inter,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
      line-height:1.5;
    }

    img{max-width:100%;display:block}
    a{text-decoration:none;color:inherit}
    button,input,textarea,select{font:inherit}

    .container{
      width:min(calc(100% - 32px), var(--max));
      margin-inline:auto;
    }

    .section{
      padding:86px 0;
    }

    .eyebrow{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:10px;
      padding:8px 14px;
      border:1px solid rgba(176,141,42,.22);
      border-radius:999px;
      background:rgba(176,141,42,.08);
      color:var(--gold-dark);
      font-size:.84rem;
      font-weight:700;
      letter-spacing:.06em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    .section-head{
      display:flex;
      align-items:end;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:20px;
      margin-bottom:28px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    .section-head h2{
      margin:10px 0 0;
      font-size:clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
      line-height:1.05;
      letter-spacing:-.03em;
    }

    .section-head p{
      margin:0;
      color:var(--muted);
      max-width:720px;
      font-size:1.02rem;
    }

    /* Header */
    .site-header{
      position:sticky;
      top:0;
      z-index:50;
      backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
      background:rgba(247,246,242,.76);
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06);
    }

    .nav{
      min-height:78px;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:20px;
    }

    .brand{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:14px;
      min-width:0;
    }

    .brand-mark{
      width:44px;
      height:44px;
      border-radius:14px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(255,255,255,.6), rgba(255,255,255,0) 35%),
        linear-gradient(145deg, var(--gold), #d8bc69 45%, var(--gold-dark));
      box-shadow:inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.4), 0 8px 18px rgba(176,141,42,.25);
      display:grid;
      place-items:center;
      color:#fff;
    }

    /* Icono de hoja (logo) */
    .brand-mark svg {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      display: block;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.2));
    }

    .brand-copy{
      min-width:0;
    }

    .brand-copy h1{
      margin:0;
      font-size:1.2rem;
      line-height:1.1;
      letter-spacing:.02em;
      font-weight:800;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    .brand-copy span{
      display:block;
      margin-top:2px;
      color:var(--gold-dark);
      font-size:.78rem;
      font-weight:600;
      letter-spacing:.04em;
    }

    .nav-links{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:24px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    .nav-links a{
      color:#2a2a2a;
      font-weight:600;
      font-size:.96rem;
    }

    .btn{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      gap:10px;
      min-height:50px;
      padding:0 20px;
      border-radius:999px;
      border:1px solid transparent;
      transition:.22s ease;
      font-weight:700;
      cursor:pointer;
    }

    .btn:hover{transform:translateY(-1px)}
    .btn-primary{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, #c8a84a 0%, var(--gold) 100%);
      color:#fff;
      box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(176,141,42,.25);
    }

    .btn-secondary{
      background:#fff;
      color:#1b1b1b;
      border-color:rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }

    .menu-toggle{
      display:none;
      width:48px;
      height:48px;
      border-radius:14px;
      border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      background:#fff;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      cursor:pointer;
    }

    /* Hero */
    .hero{
      padding:68px 0 38px;
    }

    .hero-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1.08fr .92fr;
      gap:34px;
      align-items:center;
    }

    .hero-copy h2{
      margin:18px 0 14px;
      font-size:clamp(2.7rem, 6vw, 5.3rem);
      line-height:.94;
      letter-spacing:-.05em;
    }

    .hero-copy p{
      margin:0 0 26px;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:1.08rem;
      max-width:650px;
    }

    .hero-actions{
      display:flex;
      gap:14px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      margin-bottom:26px;
    }

    .hero-points{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
      gap:14px;
    }

    .hero-point{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06);
      border-radius:18px;
      padding:16px 18px;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }

    .hero-point strong{
      display:block;
      font-size:1.15rem;
      margin-bottom:4px;
    }

    .hero-point span{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:.93rem;
    }

    .hero-visual{
      position:relative;
      min-height:620px;
    }

    .hero-card-main{
      position:absolute;
      inset:0;
      border-radius:30px;
      overflow:hidden;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,.12), rgba(0,0,0,.48)),
        url('images/hero-fragrance.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
      box-shadow:0 24px 44px rgba(0,0,0,.13);
    }

    .hero-overlay{
      position:absolute;
      left:24px;
      right:24px;
      bottom:24px;
      padding:22px;
      border-radius:22px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.10);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18);
      backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
      color:#fff;
    }

    .hero-overlay h3{
      margin:0 0 8px;
      font-size:1.45rem;
      line-height:1.05;
    }

    .hero-overlay p{
      margin:0;
      color:rgba(255,255,255,.86);
    }

    .floating-card{
      position:absolute;
      top:28px;
      right:-10px;
      width:min(280px, 72%);
      background:#fff;
      border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06);
      border-radius:22px;
      padding:18px;
      box-shadow:0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.10);
    }

    .floating-card small{
      color:var(--muted);
      display:block;
      margin-bottom:8px;
      font-weight:700;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:.08em;
    }

    .floating-card h4{
      margin:0 0 6px;
      font-size:1.08rem;
    }

    .floating-card p{
      margin:0;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:.94rem;
    }

    /* Cards */
    .grid-3{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
      gap:22px;
    }

    .grid-4{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
      gap:22px;
    }

    .card{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.78);
      border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06);
      border-radius:24px;
      overflow:hidden;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }

    .card-body{
      padding:22px;
    }

    .card h3,.card h4{
      margin:0 0 8px;
      line-height:1.05;
      letter-spacing:-.02em;
    }

    .card p{
      margin:0;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    .img-box{
      aspect-ratio:4/3;
      background:#ece8df center/cover no-repeat;
    }

    .tag{
      display:inline-flex;
      margin-bottom:12px;
      padding:7px 12px;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:rgba(176,141,42,.10);
      color:var(--gold-dark);
      font-size:.78rem;
      font-weight:800;
      letter-spacing:.06em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    /* Product cards */
    .product-card{
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      min-height:100%;
    }

    .product-card .img-box{
      aspect-ratio:1/1;
    }

    .product-card .meta{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:10px;
      margin-top:14px;
    }

    .product-card .meta span{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:.92rem;
    }

    /* Feature strip */
    .feature-strip{
      padding:28px;
      border-radius:28px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, #181818 0%, #2a2a2a 100%);
      color:#fff;
      box-shadow:0 24px 44px rgba(0,0,0,.14);
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1.1fr .9fr;
      gap:24px;
      align-items:center;
    }

    .feature-strip h3{
      margin:0 0 10px;
      font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
      line-height:1.02;
      letter-spacing:-.03em;
    }

    .feature-strip p{
      margin:0;
      color:rgba(255,255,255,.78);
      font-size:1rem;
    }

    .feature-list{
      display:grid;
      gap:12px;
    }

    .feature-item{
      display:flex;
      gap:12px;
      align-items:flex-start;
      padding:14px 16px;
      border-radius:18px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    }

    .feature-item strong{
      display:block;
      margin-bottom:4px;
    }

    .feature-item span{
      color:rgba(255,255,255,.74);
      font-size:.94rem;
    }

    /* About / process */
    .two-col{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
      gap:24px;
    }

    .panel{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.76);
      border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06);
      border-radius:26px;
      padding:28px;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }

    .steps{
      display:grid;
      gap:14px;
      margin-top:8px;
    }

    .step{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:56px 1fr;
      gap:14px;
      align-items:start;
      padding:14px;
      border-radius:18px;
      background:var(--surface-2);
    }

    .step-num{
      width:56px;
      height:56px;
      border-radius:18px;
      display:grid;
      place-items:center;
      font-weight:900;
      color:#fff;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, #c8a84a 0%, var(--gold-dark) 100%);
    }

    .step h4{
      margin:0 0 5px;
    }

    .step p{
      margin:0;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    /* Stats */
    .stats{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
      gap:18px;
    }

    .stat{
      background:#fff;
      border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06);
      border-radius:22px;
      padding:22px;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      text-align:center;
    }

    .stat strong{
      display:block;
      font-size:2rem;
      line-height:1;
      margin-bottom:8px;
      letter-spacing:-.04em;
    }

    .stat span{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:.94rem;
    }

    /* Contact */
    .contact-wrap{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1fr .95fr;
      gap:24px;
    }

    .contact-form{
      display:grid;
      gap:14px;
    }

    .field{
      display:grid;
      gap:8px;
    }

    .field label{
      font-weight:700;
      font-size:.95rem;
    }

    .field input,
    .field textarea,
    .field select{
      width:100%;
      border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.10);
      background:#fff;
      min-height:56px;
      border-radius:16px;
      padding:0 16px;
      color:var(--text);
      outline:none;
    }

    .field textarea{
      min-height:150px;
      padding:16px;
      resize:vertical;
    }

    .field input:focus,
    .field textarea:focus,
    .field select:focus{
      border-color:rgba(176,141,42,.55);
      box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(176,141,42,.10);
    }

    .contact-card{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#1b1b1b 0%, #101010 100%);
      color:#fff;
      border-radius:28px;
      padding:30px;
      box-shadow:0 24px 44px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
    }

    .contact-card h3{
      margin:0 0 12px;
      font-size:2rem;
      line-height:1.03;
      letter-spacing:-.03em;
    }

    .contact-card p{
      color:rgba(255,255,255,.76);
      margin:0 0 20px;
    }

    .contact-points{
      display:grid;
      gap:12px;
      margin:20px 0 24px;
    }

    .contact-point{
      padding:14px 16px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);
      border-radius:18px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);
    }

    .contact-point strong{
      display:block;
      margin-bottom:4px;
    }

    .contact-point span{
      color:rgba(255,255,255,.72);
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer{
      padding:24px 0 46px;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    .footer-wrap{
      border-top:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      padding-top:22px;
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:20px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      align-items:center;
    }

    .footer-links{
      display:flex;
      gap:18px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    /* Reveal animation */
    .reveal{
      opacity:0;
      transform:translateY(18px);
      transition:opacity .55s ease, transform .55s ease;
    }

    .reveal.visible{
      opacity:1;
      transform:none;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 1080px){
      .hero-grid,
      .feature-strip,
      .contact-wrap,
      .two-col{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }

      .grid-4{
        grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);
      }

      .grid-3{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }

      .stats{
        grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);
      }

      .hero-visual{
        min-height:520px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px){
      .nav-links{
        position:fixed;
        inset:78px 16px auto 16px;
        display:none;
        flex-direction:column;
        align-items:stretch;
        background:rgba(255,255,255,.96);
        border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
        border-radius:22px;
        padding:16px;
        box-shadow:0 20px 44px rgba(0,0,0,.14);
      }

      .nav-links.open{display:flex}
      .menu-toggle{display:block}
      .nav .btn-primary.nav-cta{display:none}

      .hero-points{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }

      .floating-card{
        position:static;
        margin-top:14px;
        width:100%;
      }

      .hero-visual{
        min-height:auto;
      }

      .hero-card-main{
        position:relative;
        min-height:420px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 620px){
      .section{padding:68px 0}
      .grid-4{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .stats{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .footer-wrap{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container nav">
      <a class="brand" href="#inicio" aria-label="FRESH LINER inicio">
        <div class="brand-mark">
          <!-- Icono de hoja (logo) -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M16 4C12 4 8 6 6 10C4 14 5 19 8 22C11 25 16 26 21 24C26 22 28 17 27 13C26 9 22 5 16 4Z" fill="#2B5E2B" fill-opacity="0.9"/>
            <path d="M15 8L13 13L16 15L19 13L17 8H15Z" fill="#F5E56B" />
            <circle cx="16" cy="15" r="1.5" fill="#E63946" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="brand-copy">
          <h1>FRESH LINER</h1>
          <span>Aroma style.</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <nav class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
        <a href="#inicio">Inicio</a>
        <a href="#categorias">Categorías</a>
        <a href="#productos">Productos</a>
        <a href="#empresa">Empresa</a>
        <a href="#mayoristas">Mayoristas</a>
        <a href="#contacto">Contacto</a>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contacto">Solicitar catálogo</a>
      </nav>

      <a class="btn btn-primary nav-cta" href="#contacto">Solicitar catálogo</a>
      <button class="menu-toggle" id="menuToggle" aria-label="Abrir menú">☰</button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero" id="inicio">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy reveal">
          <span class="eyebrow">Fragancias que dejan huella</span>
          <h2>Diseñamos experiencias aromáticas para auto, hogar y espacios comerciales.</h2>
          <p>
            Una web moderna para presentar la marca con fuerza, vender mejor, generar confianza y facilitar el contacto con distribuidores, clientes y puntos de venta.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#productos">Ver productos</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#contacto">Hablar con ventas</a>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-points">
            <div class="hero-point">
              <strong>Imagen premium</strong>
              <span>Diseño elegante, limpio y actual para elevar la marca.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-point">
              <strong>Mayor conversión</strong>
              <span>Llamados a la acción claros para consultas y ventas.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-point">
              <strong>GitHub Ready</strong>
              <span>Subir y publicar en GitHub Pages sin complicaciones.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-visual reveal">
          <div class="hero-card-main">
            <div class="hero-overlay">
              <h3>Fragancias que transforman ambientes</h3>
              <p>
                Auto, hogar, oficinas, retail y más. Una línea pensada para destacar por calidad, estilo y personalidad.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="floating-card">
            <small>Línea destacada</small>
            <h4>Aromatizadores premium</h4>
            <p>
              Presentación visual moderna, catálogo atractivo y sección especial para ventas mayoristas.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="categorias">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head reveal">
          <div>
            <span class="eyebrow">Categorías</span>
            <h2>Una línea completa para cada espacio</h2>
          </div>
          <p>
            Organizamos la web para que el cliente entienda rápido qué ofrece la marca y encuentre el producto ideal.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-3">
          <article class="card reveal">
            <div class="img-box" style="background-image:url('images/categoria-auto.jpg')"></div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <span class="tag">Auto</span>
              <h3>Aromatizadores para auto</h3>
              <p>Diseños atractivos, perfumes duraderos y presentación comercial de alto impacto.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card reveal">
            <div class="img-box" style="background-image:url('images/categoria-hogar.jpg')"></div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <span class="tag">Hogar</span>
              <h3>Fragancias para hogar</h3>
              <p>Difusores, sprays y soluciones aromáticas para crear una experiencia cálida y memorable.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card reveal">
            <div class="img-box" style="background-image:url('images/categoria-empresa.jpg')"></div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <span class="tag">Empresas</span>
              <h3>Espacios comerciales</h3>
              <p>Aromatización para oficinas, locales, hoteles y entornos profesionales que quieren destacar.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="productos">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head reveal">
          <div>
            <span class="eyebrow">Productos</span>
            <h2>Catálogo visual pensado para vender</h2>
          </div>
          <p>
            Reemplaza estas tarjetas por los productos reales. La estructura ya está lista para destacar fragancias, formato, uso y contacto comercial.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-4">
          <article class="card product-card reveal">
            <div class="img-box" style="background-image:url('images/producto-1.jpg')"></div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <span class="tag">Nuevo</span>
              <h4>Classic Car Fresh</h4>
              <p>Aromatizador colgante de alta rotación para punto de venta y exhibición masiva.</p>
              <div class="meta">
                <span>Uso: Auto</span>
                <a href="#contacto"><strong>Consultar</strong></a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

